%% Data Flow Diagram - CodeFlare Operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MWebhook as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant VWebhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP, 10001/TCP gRPC
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pod<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant RayClient as Ray Client

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation on OpenShift

    User->>API: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert
    API->>MWebhook: Admission Review (mutate)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    MWebhook-->>API: Patch: inject oauth-proxy sidecar,<br/>mTLS init containers, CA volumes
    API->>VWebhook: Admission Review (validate)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    VWebhook-->>API: Allowed
    API-->>User: RayCluster created

    Note over Controller,API: Controller reconciles

    Controller->>API: Create Route (ray-dashboard)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>API: Create Route (rayclient)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>API: Create OAuth Service, SA,<br/>CRB, Secrets, NetworkPolicies

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 2: Ray Dashboard Access (OpenShift OAuth)

    User->>Route: GET ray-dashboard-{cluster}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS (reencrypt)
    Route->>OAuthProxy: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    OAuthProxy-->>Route: OAuth redirect
    Note over User,OAuthProxy: User authenticates via OpenShift OAuth
    OAuthProxy->>RayHead: Proxy to dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    RayHead-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard response
    OAuthProxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Dashboard HTML

    Note over RayClient,RayWorker: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection with mTLS

    RayClient->>Route: Connect rayclient-{cluster}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS (passthrough)
    Route->>RayHead: gRPC connection<br/>10001/TCP mTLS
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Task distribution<br/>mTLS (CA-signed certs)
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Task results
    RayHead-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>RayClient: gRPC response

    Note over User,API: Flow 4: AppWrapper Workload Submission

    User->>API: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>MWebhook: Mutate AppWrapper<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    MWebhook-->>API: Mutated
    API->>VWebhook: Validate AppWrapper<br/>(SubjectAccessReview)
    VWebhook-->>API: Allowed
    Note over Controller: AppWrapper Controller creates wrapped resources
    Controller->>API: Create wrapped resources<br/>(RayClusters, Jobs, etc.)
